    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/cdc79508fe0352a1c9ac79d902d779f4.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=1170 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/cdc79508fe0352a1c9ac79d902d779f4.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这部蕴含东方武侠悲剧叙事的顶尖卡牌构筑 Roguelite 游戏即将到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兰，一位为获得巨大力量而封印自己情感的道士。你作为他善良的本我，必须面对他所引发的灾难，解开缠绕的命运之线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的《Deck Land》结合了卡牌游戏和 Roguelite 类型，提供深度单人体验，每一刻都需要新的策略。创建独特的卡组，消灭奇异的怪物，并通过卡牌融合创造无限的协同效应</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/f7929b898420d4fff0bd92923dba6d27.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=1170 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/f7929b898420d4fff0bd92923dba6d27.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要功能</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用“卡牌融合”系统，最多可融合四张卡牌，锻造出一张拥有压倒性力量的全新卡牌。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现搭配得当的融合协同效应，有效击败敌人，开辟一条无人能走的胜利之路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超越常见的像素艺术或卡通渲染，我们将专有的动态光照系统应用于精致的线条艺术（Line Art）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使在 2D 环境中，角色和背景也会实时对光影作出反应，让您体验一个沉浸感十足的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/fef02ab7f3ddb8a9f7d47b4c3ea86413.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/fef02ab7f3ddb8a9f7d47b4c3ea86413.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次挑战，路径都会分为危险和安全的路线。每一次都有新的敌人、新的卡牌和不同的首领等着你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险中发现的强大“符咒”将永久绑定，不会在游戏结束时消失。将失败转化为下一次挑战的垫脚石。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了简单的回合制战斗，使用“移动符咒”来<strong>物理躲避</strong>首领的强大攻击模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然不需要高超的技巧，但每一回合都提供了一场惊心动魄的对决，需要战略性的时机把握和移动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏讲述了一个受韩国民间故事和传说启发的悲剧故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/507fb3e4b6294933f60b12e59d9eb9bc.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/507fb3e4b6294933f60b12e59d9eb9bc.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过冒险中遇到的神秘事件，你将窥见过去的真相，揭开主角“兰”堕落的秘密，并面临命运的三个戏剧性分岔路口</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/56aef48d8a09eba09162352e89c6890d.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=1170 height=570 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/56aef48d8a09eba09162352e89c6890d.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Deck Land》演示内容：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1</strong> 个使用独特卡牌集的角色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[350+]</strong> 张完全实现的卡牌</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[100+]</strong> 种具有永久成长效果的符咒物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[10+]</strong> 种奇异的妖怪怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>[20+]</strong> 个神秘事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/5499ecb1efadf87869132c9703247674.poster.avif?t=1762582869\" width=722 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/5499ecb1efadf87869132c9703247674.webm?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322870/extras/5499ecb1efadf87869132c9703247674.mp4?t=1762582869\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
